{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"首次內容繪製","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/First_contentful_paint","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>首次內容繪製</strong> (First Contentful Paint, FCP) 是當瀏覽器從文件物件模型 (DOM) 渲染第一塊內容，第一次提供頁面正在載入的回饋給使用者。這個問題是「它發生了嗎？」當首次內容繪製完成時，答案為「是的」。</p>\n<p>首次內容繪製時間戳記是當瀏覽器第一次渲染任何文字、圖片（包含背景圖片），以及非空白的 canvas 標籤或 SVG 向量圖片。排除任何 iframe 裡的內容，但包含等待中的網路字體 (webfonts)。意即使用者第一次開始使用頁面內容。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"也可以看看","title":"也可以看看:","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/first_meaningful_paint\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">First Meaningful Paint (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/paint-timing/#first-contentful-paint\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Paint Timing specification</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"也可以看看:","id":"也可以看看"}],"summary":"首次內容繪製 (First Contentful Paint, FCP) 是當瀏覽器從文件物件模型 (DOM) 渲染第一塊內容，第一次提供頁面正在載入的回饋給使用者。這個問題是「它發生了嗎？」當首次內容繪製完成時，答案為「是的」。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"First contentful paint","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"First contentful paint","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"First contentful paint","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"First contentful paint","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/first_contentful_paint","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/first_contentful_paint/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/First_contentful_paint","title":"首次內容繪製"}],"pageTitle":"首次內容繪製 - 術語表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}